doctype 5
html

  head
    title Schola
    include headerFiles.jade
    link(rel="stylesheet", href="http://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Crimson+Text:400,700")
    link(rel="stylesheet", href="/stylesheets/recruitPage.css")
    
  body
    include navbar.jade
    div.container.notResponsive
      div.row
        div.col-xs-4
        div#recruitLetter.col-xs-8
          div.title Schola is disrupting education.
            div
              strong Join us.
          p
            | Getting into college has become 
            strong absurdly competitive. 
            | Acceptance rates for elite schools have fallen to single digits, and getting good grades simply isn't enough anymore.
          p 
            strong You
            | , among millions of 
            strong successful alumni
            | , built an entire corpus of work and expertise beating this system. Now that's locked up in your laptop, offline, and worth nothing. But it's 
            strong exactly what current students need.
          p
            | Schola is the first platform that makes this breed of academic publishing scale. Whether you're ready to 
            strong cash out 
            | on your own corpus or 
            strong impact hundreds 
            | of students at once, Schola Publisher Network is the place to start.
          p.closing Interested? Welcome aboard.
          div.input-group
            input.input-lg.form-control(type="text", placeholder="Your email address")
            span.input-group-btn
              button.btn.btn-schola.btn-lg(type="button") 
                span.glyphicon.glyphicon-send
                | Submit

    script
      var app = app || {};
      app.viewerData = {
        isLoggedIn: !{isLoggedIn},
        isSatisfier: !{isSatisfier}
      };

    include footerFiles.jade
    script
      new app.NavbarView();
